在[[足球|足球]]比赛中，如果守门员在整场比赛中未能让对手取得进球，那么就属于“零封”对手。

自[[1992–93賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|1992-93赛季]][[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]开始组建以来，已有15名门将在英超取得过100及以上场次的{{tsl|en|clean sheets|零封}}。

[[彼得·舒梅切尔|彼得·舒梅切尔]]是第一位取得百场零封成就的门将，而[[彼得·切赫|彼得·切赫]]是唯一一位保持200场零封的球员<ref name="PL stats">{{cite web|url=https://www.premierleague.com/stats/top/players/clean_sheet?co=1&se=-1&co=1&cl=-1&iso=-1&po=-1?se=-1|title=Premier League Player Stats: Clean Sheets – All Seasons|website=premierleague.com|date=2020-02-26|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711202418/https://www.premierleague.com/stats/top/players/clean_sheet?co=1&se=-1&co=1&cl=-1&iso=-1&po=-1%3Fse%3D-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他也是达成百场零封所用比赛场次最少的门将<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/11648692/martin-tylers-stats-david-de-geas-100-manchester-united-shutouts|title=Martin Tyler's stats: David de Gea's 100 Manchester United shutouts|website=Sky Sports|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015120010/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/11648692/martin-tylers-stats-david-de-geas-100-manchester-united-shutouts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

切赫保持着单赛季零封次数最多的记录，他在单赛季比赛中24次零封对手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/2651/Petr-Cech/stats?co=1&se=13|title=Petr Cech Statistics – 2004/05|accessdate=2017-12-17|work=premierleague.com|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719152313/https://www.premierleague.com/players/2651/Petr-Cech/stats?co=1&se=13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Alisson joins goalkeeping legends with clean sheets |date=2019-04-27 |url=https://www.premierleague.com/news/1199578 |website=premierleague.com |accessdate=2020-01-25 |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015140634/https://www.premierleague.com/news/1199578 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。连续零封纪录由[[埃德文·范德萨|埃德文·范德萨]]保持，他在[[2008–09賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2008-09赛季]]为[[曼联|曼联]]出战的连续14场比赛中都没有失球<ref>[https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/edwin-van-der-sar-a-career-in-pictures-2291352.html?action=gallery&ino=9 "van der Sar record"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/edwin-van-der-sar-a-career-in-pictures-2291352.html?action=gallery&ino=9 |date=20180511090052 }} 9 September 2013. Independent.</ref>。

每年，在英超赛季中零封次数最多的门将将获得[[英格兰足球超级联赛金手套奖|英格兰足球超级联赛金手套奖]]。该奖项首次颁发于[[2004–05賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2004-05赛季]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.nbcsports.com/content/premier-league-preview-top-5-goalkeepers-watch|title=Premier League Preview: Top 5 goalkeepers to watch|first=Liviu|last=Bird|date=2013-08-12|work=NBC Sports|publisher=NBC Sports Group|accessdate=2014-02-01|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218230401/http://m.nbcsports.com/content/premier-league-preview-top-5-goalkeepers-watch|archivedate=2014-02-18}}</ref>，共有七名门将赢得过金手套奖，[[乔·哈特|乔·哈特]]和彼得·切赫均获得过四次奖项，并列英超历史最多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2014-15/may/250515-sergio-aguero-and-joe-hart-seal-golden-awards-double-for-manchester-city.html|title=Aguero and Hart seal Golden Awards double for Man City|date=2015-05-25|publisher=Premier League|accessdate=2015-05-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526024954/http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2014-15/may/250515-sergio-aguero-and-joe-hart-seal-golden-awards-double-for-manchester-city.html|archivedate=2015-05-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Petr Cech: Arsenal goalkeeper wins Premier League Golden Glove award ahead of David De Gea|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/petr-cech-arsenal-news-premier-league-golden-glove-award-david-de-gea-a7035131.html|date=2016-05-18|first=Mark|last=Critchley|accessdate=2017-01-24|newspaper=The Independent|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202071614/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/petr-cech-arsenal-news-premier-league-golden-glove-award-david-de-gea-a7035131.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

